headline: These Stocks Are Moving the Most Today: Alphabet, Apple, Nvidia, Dell, XPeng, Tesla, E.W. Scripps, and More
summary: Alphabet rises after Berkshire Hathaway discloses it bought $4.3 billion worth of shares in the parent company of Google in the third quarter.
